= SDL 1.3 Support & Information =




== Support Options ==
SDL is a community-supported library.  Here are a few options if you need assistance:


=== Tutorials ===
http://wiki.libsdl.org/moin.cgi/Tutorials

Note that there is a link to SDL 1.2 tutorials here as well.

=== FAQs ===
http://wiki.libsdl.org/moin.cgi/FAQs

=== Forums ===
http://forums.libsdl.org/

Most people will find the '''SDL Development''' forum the most helpful.  This is the best place to ask technical questions that are not answered by tutorials or FAQs.  

